    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2347860/extras/spr_time_shift_drifters.png?t=1765418015\" /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Step into <i>the rift</i> where the past and future collide and only the dirtiest dirtbags survive. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get ready to brawl like never before in the ultimate online multiplayer top-down experience, <strong>Time Shift Drifters!</strong> Thrown into a warped, distant past, rise from rags to riches as a penniless warrior fighting for scraps and glory.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2347860/extras/d821f79dcd8d9e338a13ac22b54b6d84.poster.avif?t=1765418015\" width=610 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2347860/extras/d821f79dcd8d9e338a13ac22b54b6d84.webm?t=1765418015\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2347860/extras/d821f79dcd8d9e338a13ac22b54b6d84.mp4?t=1765418015\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Battle rival drifters in fast-paced PvP, or band together to survive relentless waves of the undead. Arm yourself with everything from rusty knives to flying tomatoes, and fight until you're the last one standing. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>BEWARE!</strong> The competition is fierce, and only the strongest survive. With customizable characters and diverse game types, every battle brings a new challenge. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gear up for battle and enter the arena to prove your worth; only the most ruthless drifters earn their place in time. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2347860/extras/f992e3550e30092b69b11e3d1aa7e879.webp?t=1765418015\" width=609 height=24 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Plunged into relentless arena chaos, survival belongs to the quickest and sharpest minds. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2347860/extras/0e86e8985a898521bef97c92b3bc4326.poster.avif?t=1765418015\" width=610 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2347860/extras/0e86e8985a898521bef97c92b3bc4326.webm?t=1765418015\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2347860/extras/0e86e8985a898521bef97c92b3bc4326.mp4?t=1765418015\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2347860/extras/24650dace2f9fb9ddd85c746ce7af19a.webp?t=1765418015\" width=609 height=24 /></span>Scavenge the battlefield for loot to turn the fight in your favor. Arm yourself with a fearsome arsenal of weapons, from rotten tomatoes to shields and swords. Stock up on potions to fuel your fight and overpower your adversaries. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2347860/extras/0c3adafab201d269028281f141448d52.poster.avif?t=1765418015\" width=610 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2347860/extras/0c3adafab201d269028281f141448d52.webm?t=1765418015\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2347860/extras/0c3adafab201d269028281f141448d52.mp4?t=1765418015\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2347860/extras/f05336c81de6f79428ead17267d98a7f.webp?t=1765418015\" width=609 height=24 /></span><strong> Second Counts. Every Hit Matters. </strong>Outmaneuver your foes using WASD movement and precise, cursor-based aiming. Land skill shots, dodge incoming projectiles, and use your environment to turn the tide of battle.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2347860/extras/4b4e2d68871ad73e7e929b45487707a1.poster.avif?t=1765418015\" width=610 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2347860/extras/4b4e2d68871ad73e7e929b45487707a1.webm?t=1765418015\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2347860/extras/4b4e2d68871ad73e7e929b45487707a1.mp4?t=1765418015\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2347860/extras/6cc804eea56ae7f8c5e2153eb80f578f.webp?t=1765418015\" width=609 height=24 /></span>Face relentless waves of zombies in thrilling co-op battles. Team up with fellow warriors to survive the onslaught and prove your mettle against the undead. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2347860/extras/990ba638ea1eed7d79fe5a8b819792e6.poster.avif?t=1765418015\" width=610 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2347860/extras/990ba638ea1eed7d79fe5a8b819792e6.webm?t=1765418015\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2347860/extras/990ba638ea1eed7d79fe5a8b819792e6.mp4?t=1765418015\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2347860/extras/CUSTOMIZE_YOUR_DRIFTER.png?t=1765418015\" /></span>Show off your style with customizable options for hairstyle, hair color, skin color, gender, and wardrobe. Stand out from the crowd and make your mark on the battlefield. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2347860/extras/84a00f665b968f87363f5a39ee0fa041.poster.avif?t=1765418015\" width=610 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2347860/extras/84a00f665b968f87363f5a39ee0fa041.webm?t=1765418015\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2347860/extras/84a00f665b968f87363f5a39ee0fa041.mp4?t=1765418015\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Suit up, get ready to fight for your place in history. The Rift shows no mercy...</p>",
